{"General": {"Code": "9903", "Type": "Common Stock", "Name": "Shanghai Iluvatar Corex", "Exchange": "HK", "CurrencyCode": "HKD", "CurrencyName": "Hong Kong Dollar", "CurrencySymbol": "HK$", "CountryName": "Hong Kong", "CountryISO": "HK", "OpenFigi": "BBG01ZBD68W1", "ISIN": null, "LEI": null, "PrimaryTicker": null, "CIK": null, "EmployerIdNumber": null, "FiscalYearEnd": "December", "IPODate": null, "InternationalDomestic": null, "Sector": "Technology", "Industry": "Semiconductors", "GicSector": null, "GicGroup": null, "GicIndustry": null, "GicSubIndustry": null, "Description": "Shanghai Iluvatar CoreX Semiconductor Co., Ltd. engages in the research, design, and deployment of advanced GPGPU products and AI computing solutions in China. It offers various GPGPU chips and accelerators, along with its proprietary and full-stack software development kits, including driver compiler, performance-optimized libraries, AI training frameworks and inference engines, enabling powerful AI applications across training and inference scenarios. It primarily develops and sell GPGPU accelerators, the accelerators integrate GPGPU chips with memory modules, PCB, and other critical components, forming complete computing accelerators that are ready for direct application in the end computing systems. TG Series, a training-focused product line; and ZK series, a specialized product line designed for cloud and edge inference applications. The AI Computing Solutions provides GPGPU Servers and GPGPU Clusters. The company sells its products through direct sales force and distributors. Shanghai Iluvatar CoreX Semiconductor Co., Ltd. was founded in 2015 and is based in Shanghai, China.", "Address": "Room 101, Building 3, Shanghai, China, 201210", "AddressData": {"Street": "Room 101, Building 3", "City": "Shanghai", "Country": "China", "ZIP": "201210"}, "Listings": {}, "Officers": {"0": {"Name": "Mr. Lujiang  Gai", "Title": "CEO & Executive Chairman", "YearBorn": "1982"}, "1": {"Name": "Mr. Zheng  L